<p class='Section' style='color: #8000FF;'>
 Structures of pairs {<span style='font-style: italic;color: #FF80FF;'>a</span>,<span style='font-style: italic;color: #FCE903;'>c</span>} and {<span style='font-style: italic;color: #73E600;'>b</span>,<span style='font-style: italic;color: #498FF8;'>d</span>} in abelian square-free words <span><math xmlns='http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML'
    mathematica:form='TraditionalForm'
    xmlns:mathematica='http://www.wolfram.com/XML/'>
 <msup>
  <mrow>
   <mo>(</mo>
   <msub>
